  "body": [
    "Bhai Kanwarpal Singh hails from Dehradun and is one of the senior students of Gyani Dyal Singh, who served as the principal of the Gurmat Vidyala at Rakab Ganj Sahib, Delhi since 1967. In his book ‘Gurmat Sangeet De Anmol Ratan’, Bhai Nirmal Singh Khalsa mentions that Bhai Kanwarpal Singh Ji also learned from Bhai Sarmukh Singh Fakkar. It was between 1975 and 1976 during which time Bhai Sarmukh Singh Ji was employed at Gurmat College Rishikesh. If anyone has more recordings of Bhai Kanwarpal Singh, please contact us."
